{"tid":460683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事主表明「我哋路過」仍被打","createTime":"2017-11-07T01:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T09:16:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"64cc092ae97af6238e2de056af6cc9e120571986","tid":460683,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:01:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171107/20206771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F20206771&d=XK10PQmd2BBqMv3UuF7e3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8f4097c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F20206771&h=a4c507fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171107/20206771</a><br />\n<br />\n事主表明「我哋路過」仍被打<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】事發至今近3年，鄭仲恒被打的新聞影片已廣泛傳閱，辯方表明不爭辯朱經緯就是使用警棍的人。鄭昨覆述被打的經過，他強調當晚沒有違反警方指示，但被警方踢腫「上五寸下五寸」，及遭人用警棍毆打手肘和後頸。鄭指行經亞皆老街時向警方說「唔好打，我哋路過咋」，怎料說畢幾秒頸部即被人用棍打，頓時感到「暈暈哋」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171107/large/a0103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171107%2Flarge%2Fa0103a.gif&h=70fc80a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭仲恒昨出庭覆述被打經過，當日除後頸中棍外，手肘（右圖）也有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遭警員踢「上五寸下五寸」<br />\n<br />\n鄭供稱案發2014年11月26日晚上10時許，他與女友人Rose Ma橫過馬路後，看到彌敦道與亞皆老街交界有「鳩嗚團」群眾聚集，出於好奇心兩人佇足觀望。約5分鐘後，鄭聽到該方向傳來叫囂聲，隨即有大批人群衝過來，鄭提醒Rose Ma「係時間走喇，走喇，快啲快啲」，但人群將他倆擠到牆邊，當警方趕到時，這批人群已四散。<br />\n<br />\n接着，鄭看到驅散人群的警員踢他「上五寸下五寸」，他的手肘也遭警棍打中，鄭急急向警員表示「唔好打，我哋路過咋」，並繼續沿亞皆老街前行。突然他感到後頸被打了一下，力度「大力至中等」，中棍後頓時「感到暈暈哋」。<br />\n<br />\n他護送Rose Ma離開後，折返案發現場試圖尋找施襲者但不成功，最終前往港鐵站打算離開，但站內途人看他走路不穩便上前問候，鄭遂展示頸、手肘及腿的腫脹傷勢，途人隨即買凍飲替鄭冷敷傷口。兩日後鄭仍感到「一郁就痛」，在家人建議下求診，醫生替他的傷勢拍照。醫療報告提及鄭後頸有傷勢，醫生形容為直條型的紅腫。<br />\n<br />\n鄭憶述痛楚持續了約一個月才消失。他於案發3日後即11月29日往警署投訴被打，他在律師文浩正陪同下錄取口供，其後文替他將傷勢相片及涉案新聞片段交給警方。鄭最後從報章報道得知打他的人是朱經緯。<br />\n<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t朱經緯案時序<br />\n頭條 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t外籍主控讀出「pok-guy」<br />\n頭條 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t驅佔旺鳩嗚團　涉警棍毆途人朱經緯稱真誠用武力保護自己<br />\n頭條 3小時前"},{"pid":"70597fbd36520892340457ba906f8d9c3341e5ec","tid":460683,"uid":144718,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171107/20206771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F20206771&d=XK10PQmd2BBqMv3UuF7e3Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8f4097c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F20206771&h=a4c507fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171107/20206771</a><br />\n<br />\n事主表明「我哋路過」仍被打<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】事發至今近3年，鄭仲恒被打的新聞影片已廣泛傳閱，辯方表明不爭辯朱經緯就是使用警棍的人。鄭昨覆述被打的經過，他強調當晚沒有違反警方指示，但被警方踢腫「上五寸下五寸」，及遭人用警棍毆打手肘和後頸。鄭指行經亞皆老街時向警方說「唔好打，我哋路過咋」，怎料說畢幾秒頸部即被人用棍打，頓時感到「暈暈哋」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171107/large/a0103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171107%2Flarge%2Fa0103a.gif&h=70fc80a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭仲恒昨出庭覆述被打經過，當日除後頸中棍外，手肘（右圖）也有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遭警員踢「上五寸下五寸」<br />\n<br />\n鄭供稱案發2014年11月26日晚上10時許，他與女友人Rose Ma橫過馬路後，看到彌敦道與亞皆老街交界有「鳩嗚團」群眾聚集，出於好奇心兩人佇足觀望。約5分鐘後，鄭聽到該方向傳來叫囂聲，隨即有大批人群衝過來，鄭提醒Rose Ma「係時間走喇，走喇，快啲快啲」，但人群將他倆擠到牆邊，當警方趕到時，這批人群已四散。<br />\n<br />\n接着，鄭看到驅散人群的警員踢他「上五寸下五寸」，他的手肘也遭警棍打中，鄭急急向警員表示「唔好打，我哋路過咋」，並繼續沿亞皆老街前行。突然他感到後頸被打了一下，力度「大力至中等」，中棍後頓時「感到暈暈哋」。<br />\n<br />\n他護送Rose Ma離開後，折返案發現場試圖尋找施襲者但不成功，最終前往港鐵站打算離開，但站內途人看他走路不穩便上前問候，鄭遂展示頸、手肘及腿的腫脹傷勢，途人隨即買凍飲替鄭冷敷傷口。兩日後鄭仍感到「一郁就痛」，在家人建議下求診，醫生替他的傷勢拍照。醫療報告提及鄭後頸有傷勢，醫生形容為直條型的紅腫。<br />\n<br />\n鄭憶述痛楚持續了約一個月才消失。他於案發3日後即11月29日往警署投訴被打，他在律師文浩正陪同下錄取口供，其後文替他將傷勢相片及涉案新聞片段交給警方。鄭最後從報章報道得知打他的人是朱經緯。<br />\n<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t朱經緯案時序<br />\n頭條 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t外籍主控讀出「pok-guy」<br />\n頭條 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t驅佔旺鳩嗚團　涉警棍毆途人朱經緯稱真誠用武力保護自己<br />\n頭條 3小時前</blockquote><br />\nRose ma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c92b57bea9d48d3689cb8e75aaf02d35fe0878","tid":460683,"uid":156969,"like":12,"dislike":206,"score":-194,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:03:51.000Z","msg":"講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31e46a1516fa454a69dc8e93993ad95d9fa696c","tid":460683,"uid":26570,"like":138,"dislike":3,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你收皮啦"},{"pid":"51a1e406a56b4d41ca7fbb24946e04e783b98b69","tid":460683,"uid":123969,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"外籍主控讀出「pok-guy」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本案雖然是英文審訊，但裁判官和控辯大狀均具相當中文水平。事主鄭仲恒被朱經緯擊中後向現場記者說：「仆街，我路過咋！」主控官資深大狀麥禮士幽默地顯露其半鹹淡廣東話本領照讀「pok-guy」，立即引來哄堂大笑，主任裁判官亦笑指毋須繙譯也明白當中意思。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n案件預審時由張天雁裁判官處理，審訊時交由東區法院的主任裁判官錢禮審理。錢官昨亦多番主動提醒繙譯，棍的譯法應是「rod」，而不是「pipe（管）」；「想盡快送佢走」的「送」應譯成「escort」而不是「accompany」。<br />\n另外，辯方大狀彭彼得（Peter Pannu）盤問鄭仲恒是否在中國出生，錢官笑着問辯方是甚麼意思，因為香港也是中國一部份，同樣帶來一陣笑聲，而彭亦因此轉換問法，問鄭是在中國哪個地方出生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n■記者歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"0d281aa4b3480f7e48b974c776767aa183175fd4","tid":460683,"uid":156969,"like":3,"dislike":54,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n發表下姐，咁嬲做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e800be288c60ddb221b1337fd948818eb245204","tid":460683,"uid":28563,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n發表下姐，咁嬲做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地叫你收皮，你問人地嬲唔嬲做咩？"},{"pid":"47018e4d43c7875aa4744c60a8cbba5862a7d753","tid":460683,"uid":37733,"like":6,"dislike":50,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"講下就係呀<br />\n好人好者點會係咁既時候係個到路過呀"},{"pid":"d3644de076cd8d0eab211864e008a893f6051deb","tid":460683,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34964e8962e0c32dc2aabbd3a2c85e41006f7492","tid":460683,"uid":48277,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"肯定係隻臭閪rose ma拉鄭去趁熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1781a5c0266af9e6cd2f06b2660b0ca2ab8cdff","tid":460683,"uid":39777,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:13:27.000Z","msg":"好勁，上面d巴打一定識傳心。咩證據都無就知人地一定係黎搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63bc4575684c9bf4373f6823285e93c9098960f","tid":460683,"uid":38523,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我係五毛狗<br />\n我都會好似你咁講"},{"pid":"1c3ef5077b60a1d554930386af6b67fc1d95a7d5","tid":460683,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下就係呀<br />\n好人好者點會係咁既時候係個到路過呀</blockquote><br />\n吹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c58766fc7295bea1435e7433d80ec1beeabc409","tid":460683,"uid":38523,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下就係呀<br />\n好人好者點會係咁既時候係個到路過呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五毛狗又出現了<br />\n旺角監獄來架？<br />\n去到就係犯左法？"},{"pid":"88211dd9b70ae22ff01fde783ab15ae2a77c8848","tid":460683,"uid":38523,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:17:16.000Z","msg":"十卜ching<br />\n群龍其舞<br />\n兩隻五毛狗又一齊上"},{"pid":"46d1a316dea572a1891f9c4fa1dfe813d3db163f","tid":460683,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外籍主控讀出「pok-guy」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本案雖然是英文審訊，但裁判官和控辯大狀均具相當中文水平。事主鄭仲恒被朱經緯擊中後向現場記者說：「仆街，我路過咋！」主控官資深大狀麥禮士幽默地顯露其半鹹淡廣東話本領照讀「pok-guy」，立即引來哄堂大笑，主任裁判官亦笑指毋須繙譯也明白當中意思。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n案件預審時由張天雁裁判官處理，審訊時交由東區法院的主任裁判官錢禮審理。錢官昨亦多番主動提醒繙譯，<span style=\"color: red;\">棍的譯法應是「rod」，而不是「pipe（管）」；「想盡快送佢走」的「送」應譯成「escort」而不是「accompany」。</span><br />\n另外，辯方大狀彭彼得（Peter Pannu）盤問鄭仲恒是否在中國出生，錢官笑着問辯方是甚麼意思，因為香港也是中國一部份，同樣帶來一陣笑聲，而彭亦因此轉換問法，問鄭是在中國哪個地方出生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n■記者歐陽聯發</blockquote><br />\n有幸見過錢禮本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618cd2c6bbbf812ee6bc7ef6004285e0fee15b87","tid":460683,"uid":47359,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下就係呀<br />\n好人好者點會係咁既時候係個到路過呀</blockquote><br />\n好人好姐點解做五毛呀十卜ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885129af2556307dc205fe369b498328be7a9684","tid":460683,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講下就係呀<br />\n好人好者點會係咁既時候係個到路過呀</blockquote><br />\n吹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c736eefe38872d18d8befa9fa18defe73c674680","tid":460683,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:27:39.000Z","msg":"屌你個rosema"},{"pid":"446c2b738a558a7215b64280eb5bfc7d24091f4f","tid":460683,"uid":51937,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我係五毛狗<br />\n我都會好似你咁講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6922e205513fa0f38abf74a4aaa368a287d279ae","tid":460683,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我係五毛狗<br />\n我都會好似你咁講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8deef7d19dc8bfb3e2505b0bced2a741b37c9bb","tid":460683,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真如果我搞事，差佬黎到我都會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我係五毛狗<br />\n我都會好似你咁講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93130a91091ab997fa396a6